Uses of Package
cz.syntea.xdef.model

  • Packages that use cz.syntea.xdef.model 
    Package Description
    cz.syntea.xdef
    Contains interfaces for processing of X-definitions and the factory for compilation of X-definitions and creation of some important objects used in X-definitions.
    cz.syntea.xdef.component
    Provides tools for the X-components technology.
    cz.syntea.xdef.model
    Provides USER INTERFACE for accessing to XMDefinition objects (models).
    cz.syntea.xdef.proc
    Contains interfaces used in external methods.
